Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper deals with textual data analysis and classification. 
- cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is also likely as the paper focuses on identifying potential patterns of human trafficking activities which manifest online and identifying advertisements of high interest to law enforcement. 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is relevant as the paper deals with crawling and analyzing data from a website. 
- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) is relevant as the paper deals with identifying patterns of human trafficking activities which may involve social networks. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is relevant as the paper proposes a semi-supervised learning method for the task at hand.
